        "text_KAgD8r": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h2><strong>Buy Best Perfume for Men</strong></h2><h3>Why Perfume Matters for Men</h3><p>Perfume is more than just a scent. It’s an extension of your personality. The right fragrance makes an impression before you say a word. Your scent lingers long after you’ve walked away in a world that moves fast. That’s why finding the best perfume for men isn’t about a fleeting trend – it’s about identity.</p><p>Ludic understands it. And enacts it. We’ve curated a collection of fragrances that speak to every mood and moment, especially for men. What do you want to be? A mysterious night owl or an all-day adventurer? Ludic has crafted a bottle that matches the vibe with every man. Let us present our top men’s perfumes for 2025, helping you find a fragrance that feels true to your personality and presence.</p><h3><strong>Understanding Types of Perfume for Men</strong></h3><p>Which perfume is the best for men? Knowing which type of perfume suits your needs can help you make a smarter choice. </p><p><strong>Eau de Parfum (EDP)</strong>: High fragrance concentration. Long-lasting, perfect for evening events or special occasions.</p><p><strong>Eau de Toilette (EDT)</strong>: Lighter and more refreshing. Ideal for day-to-day wear.</p><p><strong>Body Spray</strong>: Quick, light application. Perfect post-gym or on the go.</p><p><strong>Roll-On</strong>: Discreet and travel-friendly. Great for quick touch-ups without overspraying.</p><p><strong>Practical Tip</strong>: The best way to use Eau de Parfum is for formal dinners or date nights. Go for Eau de Toilette at work or classes. Body sprays work well when you're heading outdoors or need a refresher. Roll-ons are your best friend during travel.</p><p>When selecting a perfume for men, consider where you'll be. How long you'll be out and what impression you want to leave.</p>",
            "mobile_content": "",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
