        "collapsible_row_fVHKwQ": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "1. Leather by Ludic",
            "icon": "check_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>A bold and confident scent, <a href=\"https://ludic.life/collections/fragrances/products/leather\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Leather by Ludic</span></a> speaks volumes. With top notes of raspberry, saffron, and thyme, Leather quickly deepens into olibanum and jasmine, settling into a luxurious base of suede, amber, and woody notes. It's made for night-time appeal and indelible impressions. If you walk into a room to be noticed, Leather is your signature.</p><p><strong>Best for</strong>: Night outs, formal events, special evenings<br/><strong>Longevity</strong>: 8–10 hours</p><p><strong>Price: </strong>₹699</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_mjpJ4r": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "2. Coast by Ludic",
            "icon": "check_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>Fresh, energetic, and full of life. <a href=\"https://ludic.life/collections/fragrances/products/coast\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Coast for Men</span></a> is built for sun-filled adventures with zesty grapefruit, mandarin orange and petitgrain. Seaweed and rosemary keep things breezy, while amber and cedar add subtle warmth. It is the best smelling perfume for men to thrive on movement and freshness.</p><p><strong>Best for</strong>: Daytime, office, travel, casual meetups<br/><strong>Longevity</strong>: 6–8 hours</p><p><strong>Price: </strong>₹699</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_UdhVLj": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "3. CSK Marina by Ludic",
            "icon": "check_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>A sporty, all-purpose fragrance, <a href=\"https://ludic.life/collections/fragrances/products/marina-for-men\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Marina by Ludic</span></a> is the best male perfume yet. It opens with cardamom and petitgrain, flows through juniper and ends on tonka bean and sandalwood. Clean and breezy, it fits every setting without overpowering the moment.</p><p><strong>Best for</strong>: Daily use, college, office<br/><strong>Longevity</strong>: 5–7 hours</p><p><strong>Price: </strong>₹899</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_69p6DQ": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "4. CSK Kaaram by Ludic",
            "icon": "check_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>Kaaram stays true as the best male perfume. It is Spicy and assertive. Pink pepper, grapefruit, cinnamon, and saffron meet with leathery and smoky undertones. <a href=\"https://ludic.life/collections/fragrances/products/kaaram\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Kaaram by Ludic</span></a> is for the bold – it makes a statement and doesn’t fade into the background.</p><p><strong>Best for</strong>: Club nights, winter wear, celebrations<br/><strong>Longevity</strong>: 7–9 hours</p><p><strong>Price: </strong>₹899</p>",
